Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishō Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Comment: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP end}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Benio was set on trying to learn the ways of femininity while Shinobu is away from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden, he's deployed to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming that this was yet another scheme of Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,she once again headed \Nto the 1st Division headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she was surprised to discover that Innen had also been transferred to Manchuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With nothing else she could do, she decided to pray for Shinobu's safety
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by promising not to touch any more alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:51.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H212A2D&\3c&HE7DDDC&\blur1.001}Abstinence {禁酒}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some strange reason, the Count and Countess \Nwere in the mood to do nothing but drink that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So abstaining proved very depressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but then she received \Nher first letter from Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be waiting inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! T-That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've suddenly grown so handsome, Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings sure work in mysterious ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is a special case, Boss. {lit: it's because you're special - meaning I don't see you as a woman... probably.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! A letter from Young Master arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did he write?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know... \NAh, I'm so curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? I can't be thinking about work at such a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss! Aren't you gonna read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Shinobu... A letter from Shinobu!{If these 2 phrases are separate, it's weird to see the text move and the ellipsis change to an exclamation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,600)}Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:07.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1.001\pos(721.99,104.8)\fade(0,100)\c&HD9E2DE&}Episode 27 \N {\fs120}Red Sunset in Siberia{赤い夕日のシベリアで}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a letter from Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What did he write?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, I haven't read it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent that letter to Benio, not to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. \NEven I'm waiting patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he send me one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize. I'll let you know as soon as I read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter is for my eyes only!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio! Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the letter you've received \Nfrom Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it while that monstrosity is staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think me too ugly an audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he wrote to me... Ah, my heart is racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Count!{/G-Grandfather!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whisper it just to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, open it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! I should be the first one to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C7C74&\3c&HE0D6D5&\fs100.001\pos(687,260)}Futon Room{布団部屋}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like a good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, hurry up and read it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! B-Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the first to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H231DC4&\blur1.5\bord0\fs100.001\pos(347,306)\frz72.6}Wham!{ドン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Lady Benio,\Nshow me the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to do it outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the letter to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Did he write anything to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Or about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with everyone? \NThis letter is for {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a quiet place, \Nor else I'll never read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot about one place that could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too late.{\i0}{ep 25, 17:25}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Benio.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've chosen to spend my life with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm willing to face with you\Nany curveballs fate throws your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinobu... Don't joke like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've loved you ever since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't left my mind \Never since you told me those words.{"always ... since" is somewhat contradictory.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru! Chimaru! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Tenmaru! \NTenmaru, you bad dog! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!\NI said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! \NIt's because the letter smells of Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are his dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just smelling Shinobu \Nis enough for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's in there? \NLet me see, let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.20,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3925D7&\fs100.001\bord1.001\blur1.001\fade(0,500)\pos(308.999,320)}Slam! {バタム - not sure actually}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place where I can be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE6E0E2&\pos(461,468)\fs79.999\bord1.001\blur1.001}Rustle {/secretly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of the Russian wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Russian wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know the fragrances of the farm. {/countryside}{i have no idea what he says tbh but the message is more or less that}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2129C4&\3c&H68D6DD&\fs120\blur1}Wham! {ガン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Benio, are you doing well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been sent here all of a sudden, \Nthat must've spooked everyone a great deal, hasn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I am doing fine here, \Nso don't you worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been two weeks since I've arrived to Siberia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(601,280)\fade(790,0)\blur1.001\c&H17402E&\3c&H54BA83&}Siberia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our unit is far away from the actual battlefield, so it's pretty quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I'm writing this letter, when I look out of the window to collect my thoughts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there are wide plains for as far as the eye can see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now I'm only in a small section of Europe,{\i0}{seems he calls eurasia collectively "europe"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's more than enough to sense the immensity of Siberia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd love to show you this breathtaking scenery. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.94,Top,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can clearly picture you running around these fields, cheerful as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wink! {sore}{lol, katyusha in 1920?}
