Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, there's one more thing that might interest you, my dear heavy drinker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here they have a very strong spirit called Vodka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:27.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0A2439&\3c&H1FBEDC&\blur1.001\fs79.999\fax-0.042764\fscx126.69\fscy124.88\frz1.3679\frx-6.6992\fry-1.6781\xbord0.00\ybord0.00\org(1158.46,832.81)\pos(1160.62,782.87)}Vodka
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet you're drooling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! How could he tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking her quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I wonder if she's eaten something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This flower grows in the wasteland. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The locals call it Malinka. {nobody says malinka instead of malina goddamnit}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Siberia's short summers, these flowers bloom and cover entire fields.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I picked one because it reminded me of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Malinka... raspberry flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the wastelands of Siberia, \NI hope that you, just like this flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can spend your days carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}P.S. This war is silly and \Nit has nothing to with Japan, {/has nothing to do with japan}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I might end up coming back home earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}P.P.S. That day, I'll bring many bottles of vodka for us to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look forward to it, okay?\NSincerely yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief... \Nit's such a relief to hear that he's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His unit is not on the front line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gimme a break! {mou iya}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.03,Top,,0,0,0,,Banzai, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god! Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely, lovely! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vodka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H131C10&\3c&HD7D8D3&\blur1.001}Abstinence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1087,60)\c&H000C30&\3c&H3BB2EA&}Abstinence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, Benio! \NYou swore that you'd abstain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, Count and Countess \Ncan't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I see. I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! What in the world did Shinobu write to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, he said that his unit is not in a dangerous place, \Nso we don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! That's such good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's good. That's the most important thing.\NBut tell me, what did he write about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh no... He only wrote about me here - \Nthere's not even a word about anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means... \NI'm all Shinobu can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's so funny in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what he wrote about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what about me? Hurry up, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what should I do? \NHe wrote nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this has only become \Nmore troublesome.{Is she pretending to be the narrator here or something? Revert this change if so.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stop dawdling and read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is grandfather as grumpy as usual?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grandfather may seem grumpy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but in reality he just needs company at all times, so please be kind to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So he said that about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grandmother has frail health and often falls ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so I trust you to look after her in my place."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd he ever write about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure, sure. \NRight here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ms. Kisaragi is the backbone of the Ijuuin family:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without her, nothing would work the way it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thus I hope that she lives long and serves the Ijuuin family for years to come."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I promise that... I promise that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll serve you until the day I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ranmaru," err, I mean, "Ranko and Ushigorou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are your right-hand and left-hand men and I hope they continue to to boost our family's morale."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the goldfish-tattooed Ushigorou, \Nswear on my life that I won't let you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Tenmaru and Chimaru are eager to know what he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please tell Tenmaru and Chimaru to keep being good dogs and to protect the Ijuuin family."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder to fool animals than people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time to write my response to Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...\N"I'm currently abstaining from alcohol,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so, instead of vodka, \Nbring some raspberry jam, okay?" {actually says "strawberry" but I think they got completely confused, having to deal with malinka which is raspberry}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fs120\pos(895.001,8)\c&HE0E0E2&}Whoops!{はた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always end up talking about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I write?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the honorable Ijuuin Shinobu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is way too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"With respect, to Mr. Shinobu."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that sets the wrong mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"My beloved Shinobu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I originally came here to make a mess of this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what it came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, go ahead and swing it, please.{ep 16, 3:21}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-Accept your fate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This duel ends in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Benio's victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm spinning round!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs130\c&H232AC4&\3c&H70D5DC&\blur1.001}Wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up! Let go of me! Hey!{\i0}{ep 19 5:08}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that your marriage with Young Master \Nwill be the one that stands the test of time.{\i0}{ref: ep 22, 16:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Kichiji...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally realized that Shinobu is a good person!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Banzai! Banzai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What's with that disgraceful look!{\i0}{ep 23, 3:09}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I love my dear Kisaragi too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, I ended up dozing off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's the drool stain proving it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H29394B&\3c&HE1D9D8&\b0\blur1.001}Anyway, I ended up dozing off.\NHere's the drool stain proving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio never changes, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I get to laugh so heartily ever since I left Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my High Collar Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. A letter from his girlfriend. My, oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lieutenant's actin' too affected, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta be honest, \NI just can't stand him and his blond hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it ridiculous that he's our officer even though he's got no real experience in the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn if our unit is led by someone like him. \NWe'll be doomed when push comes to shove.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a surprise, \Nwe're all outcast rogues ourselves, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, chill out, Onijima, are you really gonna drink this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how about getting him into some trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll poke fun at that pretentious officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Garrison Commander Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When did they send you to Manchuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, is it Second Lieutenant Ijuuin's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've set him up with the worst rogues out there.\NHe'll have a hard time controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before something happens to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, fall in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bud, did you hear anything just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was just a mosquito buzzing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. If you don't want to listen to me, I'll force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.\NYou have some nerve speaking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to, since it's the only \Nlanguage you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're made of stronger stuff than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected a Tokyoite, \Nwet behind the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that I'll back down after this scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him, Onijima!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's help Onijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NIn Ijuuin's squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always those thugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, what the hell is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin, step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You five stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you even doing, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:26.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H663D05&\bord5\blur1.001\fs100.001\pos(224.84,12.36)}Smack {バシッ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you came here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Corporal punishments were an everyday occurrence\Nin the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it was very rare for officers to be punished before their subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If that ever happened, his authority would undoubtedly be eroded,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,like what Shinobu is facing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me why, won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you embarrassed to stand before soldiers who've fought in battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, they spotted us so soon.  \NWay to spoil the fun. {/he intervened}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and say it, Second Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no stranger to the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant! Who started this brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you can say who.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shinobu reports his subordinates' lack of discipline, he'll escape harm and Onijima will be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What choice will our blond Second Lieutenant make?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Either of them probably \Nwould've caused Benio to cry. {idk -国じゃベニオが泣いてます - same, no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,While Shinobu is away, \NBenio is still set on her goal:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To become as feminine as possible.\NBut it's not an easy path. {CMS: "When, however, a colon introduces one or more complete sentences, ... the first word that follows the colon should be capitalized"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfecting skills like making tea and arranging flowers may be out of her reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon realizing that, the Count decides to take her to a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this will also end in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0}\N"A Battle for Men, A Battle for Women."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it! {ngl, I fell off my chair when this line came about - perevodildo}
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
